title: Coaches as pro wrestlers: 2020 draft
description:
Time once again for the college football internet's single most reliable content: PICKING COACHES WHO SHOULD FIGHT EACH OTHER
Holly, Jason, and Spencer are each managing their own stables, drafting FBS head coaches to build five-man tag teams
You, the Podcast Readership, have also filled out a draft board and get a five-coach team of your own
Ryan is not here, so we're giving him all the lowest-voted coaches from your draft board
Ryan's team will be competing for the Intercontinental title at absolute most
Tell a friend about our stupid podcast!
